The ''[[Ruckus Wireless]]'' logo (dog version), "2012 Ruckus Wireless Inc.", "GD 38" :and "Pocket Dog" is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos. :"FAB 100-11224-001 REV A" is on the other side of the board. "Ruckus Wireless" and "100-11238-001 REV A" is silkscreened on two of the antennas.
The manual specifies the model as ''ZoneFlex'' 7351-U (presumably a sub-model w/ a USB port).
